>> Execute regressions should run against the same local agent shape the
>> benchmark entrypoints use: planner metadata kept on `tools`, live
>> `var tools` collection passed separately, and no `@rigBuild` round
>> trip in between. That keeps the test focused on execute compilation
>> and runtime dispatch rather than on the separate opaque-handle path.
